    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Yes, use the object-oriented interface to reuse a plot across cells, or you can actually turn off the automatic per-cell cleanup of figures, and rely on yourself to close/open figures with:\n\n```\n%config InlineBackend.close_figures=False\n```\n"
